name: Birds Of Paradise Inspired tee
description:
LIMITED EDITION TEE!

Sublimation all over print shirt made of 100% polyester with a cotton feel.

Please note that these t shirts are made to order, by the 12/09/13 all orders will be sent to be made and then will be shipped when ready.

Understand that the making and shipping process may take between 5-14 days.

For international shipping, please contact prior to buying.

The t shirts are slim fitting, to get the best look it is recommended that you go one size larger as the garment is meant to be worn 'oversized'.

More photographs of the t shirt can be found on our tumblr page:

http://fixedclothingco.tumblr.com/tagged/BirdsofParadise
